@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_dwakci(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v0 = (wp.cos(0.80) - (0.92 - wp.sin(v0 + 0.14)))
    tmp = (tmp * wp.cos(wp.abs(v0 + 0.86)))
    v2 = v1
    v2 = (wp.cos(tmp) * (v1 - v1))
    v0 = (wp.exp(wp.exp(v0 + 0.23)) - (wp.cos(v2 + 0.55) + (v0 + 0.97 * v1 + 0.12)))
    v2 = wp.exp(0.26)
    v0 = (wp.abs(0.16) * wp.sin(0.19))
    v1 = v2
    data[tid] = v0
